  "prompt": "Where can I found highly experienced and qualified horse riding instructors in Melbourne?",
  "response": "In Melbourne, you can find highly experienced and qualified horse riding instructors at several reputable riding schools and facilities. Here are some places to consider:\n\n1. **Melbourne International Equestrian Centre** - Offers a range of programs from beginner to advanced levels with certified coaches.\n\n2. **Equestrian Victoria** - A governing body that can provide information on accredited riding instructors and schools throughout Melbourne.\n\n3. **The Riding School** - Located in Ivanhoe, this school offers lessons for all ages and skill levels with experienced instructors.\n\n4. **Glenhaven Park Equestrian Centre** - Known for its professional instructors and comprehensive programs for both beginners and advanced riders.\n\n5. **Karkarook Park Riding School** - Offers lessons from qualified instructors in a friendly environment.\n\n6. **Melbourne Horse Riding Adventures** - Provides a range of riding experiences and lessons with qualified guides.\n\n7. **Local Equestrian Clubs** - Many clubs have qualified instructors and can offer lessons, including the Melbourne Equestrian Centre.\n\nWhen selecting an instructor or riding school, consider factors like their qualifications, experience, reviews from other students, and whether they offer the type of riding you are interested in (e.g., dressage, jumping, trail riding). It can also be helpful to visit the facility and meet the instructors before making a decision.",
